Tom: Hi, Anna. What did you do yesterday?
Anna: I went to the park with my mom.
Tom: That sounds fun! What did you do there?
Anna: I played with my ball and I ran on the grass.
Tom: Did you climb the big tree?
Anna: No, I didn't, because it was too high.
Tom: I went to the park too, but it started to rain.
Anna: Oh no! So what did you do then?
Tom: I went home and watched TV.
Anna: Next time, let's play together!
